  #set text(size: 11pt)
  #strong[Poster demo]

  This sample is meant to make the preview pane look less like a plain article.

  - warm paper-like background
  - centered marketing copy
  - simple card layout
]

#v(0.8cm)

#text(size: 12pt, weight: "bold")[Why it is useful]

